title: Images of April
text:
Images of April 1:51pm BST - 01:38
Images taken by Reuters photographers around the world in April 2018, including the inter-Korean summit, deadly protests on the Gaza-Israel border, a migrant caravan seeking asylum in the U.S. and the Toronto van attack. Produced by David Lucas. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
